attachments.title: Long-Awaited Eastside Sports Bar With Massive Rooftop Patio Finally Sets an Opening Date
attachments.text: It seems we’ve been waiting for Century Bar for about a century. The enormously ambitious, massive Central Eastside sports bar and event space from the owners of Dig-a Pony, Bye and Bye and Jackknife was announced in January 2015.
